coal producer, said it has nominated former  Vostok Nafta
Investment Ltd. (VNIL)  director Alex Williams as an independent board
member.  Williams was a director at Vostok Nafta until 2006, helping
the Swedish company develop its Russian business and working to
improve corporate governance at the countryâ€™s oil companies,
Kuzbass Fuel said in an e-mailed statement today. After Vostok
Nafta, Williams worked as an investment manager at Varyag
